title: Watch: Dal Shabet’s Subin Releases MVs For Beautiful Solo Tracks “Circle’s Dream” And “Strawberry”
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
Dal Shabet’s Subin has released two stunning new songs! 
On February 23 at midnight KST, the talented artist shared the music videos for her two new tracks, “Circle’s Dream” and “Strawberry,” off her new digital single “Circle’s Dream.” 
Subin’s title track is a pop song with a catchy beat that is bound to get listeners bouncing along, while she takes things slower in the ballad “Strawberry.” Both tracks highlight both her gorgeous voice! 
Check them out below.
